headline: No classes for Palestinian children as Israel shuts six UN-run schools in East Jerusalem
description: Six schools run by the United Nations Relief and Works Agency for Palestine Refugees (UNRWA) in the eastern part of the city have been closed by Israeli authorities. Nearly 600 children now face being left out of school.
